<h2 class="text-title">Space between columns</h2>

<p>This use a border-left on cols except the first and the last. Avoid it if possible and use a padding inside the col.</p>

<div class="row spaced align-center">
    <div class="wp-50" style="background: red"><div style="background: #AAF">50%</div></div>
    <div class="wp-50" style="background: red"><div style="background: #AFA">50%</div></div>
</div>
<br>
<div class="row spaced align-center">
    <div class="wp-33" style="background: red"><div style="background: #AAF">33%</div></div>
    <div class="wp-33" style="background: red"><div style="background: #AFA;">33%</div></div>
